The paper discusses the design and implementation of a system for secure distribution of sensitive data, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The system also incorporates a generic framework that allows different applications to distribute data, which could fall under the categories of social networks (cs.SI), data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), and cryptography (cs.CY).
